						<div class="postbody">My responses to these questions got rather wordy and started to further depart from the original post on 8x8 attrs so I've decided to answer these questions in a separate <a href="https://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=9&amp;t=17247" class="postlink">thread</a>.</div>

					
